text: Ness Ashby Murby (born 4 October 1985) is an Australian-born Canadian Paralympic athlete who competes in discus throw and javelin throw events in international level events. Murby has represented Australia in goalball between 2005 and 2007. ==References== Category:1985 births Category:Living people Category:Paralympic track and field athletes of Canada Category:Canadian female discus throwers Category:Canadian female javelin throwers Category:Athletes (track and field) at the 2016 Summer Paralympics
